    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🎂 Birthday Bot Flow\n\n**Triggers:**\n- 18:30 UTC → 00:00 IST (India)\n- 23:00 UTC → 00:00 IE (summer DST)\n- 00:00 UTC → 00:00 IE (winter)\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Determine country & date\n2. Fetch active contacts from Supabase\n3. Filter to today's birthdays (handles Feb 29)\n4. Check if already sent today (idempotent)\n5. Generate personalized message via DeepSeek\n6. Send via Evolution API (retry up to 3x)\n7. Log success or failure\n8. On failure → alert admins\n\n**Before activating:**\n- Replace `YOUR_EVOLUTION_URL` and `YOUR_INSTANCE_NAME` in both HTTP Request nodes\n- Set up 3 credentials (see README)\n- Run the Supabase schema SQL",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 400
      },
